Paper: hep-th/9507159

Date: 1995-07-28

Title: Critical equation of state from the average action

Authors: J. Berges, N. Tetradis and C. Wetterich

Comments: Latex, 8 pages, 2 uuencoded figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev.Lett. 77 (1996) 873-876

The scaling form of the critical equation of state is computed for$O(N)$-symmetric models. We employ a method based on an exact flow equation fora coarse grained free energy. A suitable truncation is solved numerically.